      <Quotations id="ritualQuotations">
         <ab><ab>Nērang VVrS0.3 (Nērang ī āb) [mss. 4000 4010 4020 4025 4063], cf. WiD and Revāyat of Kāma Bohra (MU1, p. I. 577), on the Nērang ī Āb ud Padyāb ceremony:</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">(Pahl.) dudīgar bār hamāg xūb bē nigerišn u-š ātaxš gāh šustan u-š dast pad pādyāb āwāz kardan </ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">For the second time (the Zōt) hast to cast a glance well at all and he should wash the fire-stand and purify his hands.</ab></ab>
      </Quotations>
